views.submit_action_message: Thank you for adding this criterium

fields.name: Price category
fields.formula: filter(if(field('Starting price (USD)') < lookup('Criteria','Threshold low'),lookup('Criteria','Tag low'),if(field('Starting price (USD)') >= lookup('Criteria','Threshold high'),lookup('Criteria','Tag high'), lookup('Criteria','Tag medium'))), lookup('Criteria','Name') = 'Price')

fields.name: Horsepower category
fields.formula: filter(if(field('Horsepower') < lookup('Criteria','Threshold low'),lookup('Criteria','Tag low'),if(field('Horsepower') >= lookup('Criteria','Threshold high'),lookup('Criteria','Tag high'), lookup('Criteria','Tag medium'))), lookup('Criteria','Name') = 'Powerful engine')

fields.name: Fuel consumption category
fields.formula: filter(if(field('Average GPM') < lookup('Criteria','Threshold low'),lookup('Criteria','Tag low'),if(field('Average GPM') >= lookup('Criteria','Threshold high'),lookup('Criteria','Tag high'), lookup('Criteria','Tag medium'))), lookup('Criteria','Name') = 'Fuel consumption')

fields.name: Total score
fields.formula: field('Price score') + field('Horsepower score') + field('Fuel consumption score') + field('Distance score')

fields.name: Price score
fields.formula: sum(filter(if(field('Starting price (USD)') < lookup('Criteria','Threshold low'),lookup('Criteria','Value low') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'),if(field('Starting price (USD)') >= lookup('Criteria','Threshold high'),lookup('Criteria','Value high') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'), lookup('Criteria','Value medium') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'))), lookup('Criteria','Name') = 'Price'))

fields.name: Horsepower score

fields.name: Fuel consumption score
fields.formula: sum(filter(if(field('Average GPM') < lookup('Criteria','Threshold low'),lookup('Criteria','Value low') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'),if(field('Average GPM') >= lookup('Criteria','Threshold high'), lookup('Criteria','Value high') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'), lookup('Criteria','Value medium') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'))), lookup('Criteria','Name') = 'Fuel consumption'))

fields.formula: sum(filter(if(field('Calculated space') < lookup('Criteria','Threshold low'),lookup('Criteria','Value low') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'),if(field('Calculated space') >= lookup('Criteria','Threshold high'),lookup('Criteria','Value high') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'), lookup('Criteria','Value medium') * lookup('Criteria','Importance'))), lookup('Criteria','Name') = 'Capacity'))
